Q.4
Predict the output of following Java program

class Main { 
   public static void main(String args[]) { 
      try { 
         throw 10; 
      } 
      catch(int e) { 
         System.out.println("Got the  Exception " + e); 
      } 
  } 
} 
(A) Got the Exception 10
(B) Got the Exception 0
(C) Compiler Error

Answer: (C)
